memberdef.name: BO_PARAM
memberdef.initializer: static constexpr Type Name() { return Value; }

memberdef.name: BO_REQUIRED_PARAM
memberdef.initializer: static const Type Name() \ { \ static_assert(false, "You need to define the parameter:" #Name " !"); \ return Type(); \ }

memberdef.name: BO_DYN_PARAM
BO_PARAM_ARRAY
memberdef.initializer: static Type Name(size_t i) \ { \ assert(i < __VA_NARG__(__VA_ARGS__)); \ static constexpr Type _##Name[] = {__VA_ARGS__}; \ return _##Name[i]; \ } \ static constexpr size_t Name##_size() \ { \ return __VA_NARG__(__VA_ARGS__); \ } \ typedef Type Name##_t;

memberdef.name: BO_PARAM_VECTOR
memberdef.initializer: static const Eigen::Matrix<Type, __VA_NARG__(__VA_ARGS__), 1> Name() \ { \ static constexpr Type _##Name[] = {__VA_ARGS__}; \ return Eigen::Map<const Eigen::Matrix<Type, __VA_NARG__(__VA_ARGS__), 1>>(_##Name); \ }

memberdef.name: BO_PARAM_STRING
memberdef.initializer: static constexpr const char* Name() { return Value; }

memberdef.name: BO_PARAMS
memberdef.initializer: struct Ps__ { \ Ps__() \ { \ static std::string __params = #P; \ boost::replace_all(__params, ";", ";\n"); \ boost::replace_all(__params, "{", "{\n"); \ Stream << "Parameters:" << __params << std::endl; \ } \ }; \ P; \ static Ps__ ____p;
